                  <Icon name="lucide:phone" class="h-5 w-5" aria-hidden="true" />
                  <span>Suna Acum</span>
                </a>
                <a
                  href="https://maps.app.goo.gl/HzDLuMR94Fq9fSYU8"
                  target="_blank"
                  rel="noopener noreferrer"
                  class="inline-flex items-center justify-center gap-2 rounded-full bg-slate-100 px-5 py-2.5 text-base font-bold uppercase tracking-wide text-slate-700 transition hover:bg-slate-200"
                  aria-label="Vezi pe harta"
                >
                  <Icon name="lucide:map-pin" class="h-5 w-5" aria-hidden="true" />
                  <span>Harta</span>
                </a>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>

      <section id="faq" class="col-span-1 rounded-2xl bg-white p-7 ring-1 ring-slate-100 sm:col-span-2">
        <div class="mb-6 flex items-center gap-2">
          <Icon name="lucide:help-circle" class="h-6 w-6 text-[#2563eb]" aria-hidden="true" />
          <h3 class="font-heading text-2xl font-bold text-slate-900">Intrebari Frecvente</h3>
        </div>
        <div class="space-y-6 text-lg leading-relaxed text-slate-600">
          <div class="border-b border-slate-100 pb-4">
            <h4 class="text-lg font-semibold text-slate-900">Cat dureaza o reparatie?</h4>
            <p>
              Majoritatea operatiunilor (schimb display, baterie) se realizeaza <strong>pe loc</strong> (30-60 minute) daca piesa este pe stoc. Pentru interventii complexe pe placa de baza, timpul poate varia intre 24-48h.
            </p>
          </div>
          <div class="border-b border-slate-100 pb-4">
            <h4 class="text-lg font-semibold text-slate-900">Oferiti garantie?</h4>
            <p>
              Da! Oferim garantie intre <strong>3 si 12 luni</strong> pentru orice piesa inlocuita si pentru manopera. Bonul fiscal si certificatul de garantie se ofera pe loc.
            </p>
          </div>
          <div>
            <h4 class="text-lg font-semibold text-slate-900">Se pierd datele din telefon?</h4>
            <p>
              In 99% din cazuri (schimb display, baterie, mufa), datele tale raman intacte. Totusi, recomandam intotdeauna un backup preventiv inainte de a veni in service.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
